 Description:
 The Cooperative Engagement Capability (CEC) AN/USG-2B system provides real time integration of fire control quality sensor data into a single composite data source, which is used by multiple CEC ships
 and airborne units for direct and remote missile engagements. CEC significantly improves battle force Anti-Air Warfare (AAW) capability by coordinating all force AAW sensors into a single real time, fire control
 quality composite track picture.

