 Description:
 The Multi Function Radar (MFR) element supports the DDG 1000 system in achieving Integrated Air and Surface Dominance with the capability to neutralize hostile surface vessels and aircraft at short ranges.
 The MFR is comprised of X-Band (AN/SPY-3) arrays integrated through a common signal data processor offering surface and horizon search capabilities and 3-D air search radar capabilities. The X-Band
 portion also has two navigation modes (high power and lower power) for use in piloting and marine navigation.

