 Elements. The CAPS is a distributed power system designed to operate from the ship-supplied medium voltage distribution Integrated Power System's (IPS) 13.8 kV AC power source. The CAPS consists of
 two Power Distribution Units (PDUs) and four Power Conversion Units (PCUs).

