 Description:
 The Electro-Optical / Infrared (EO/IR) Sensor Suite Element is composed of both the hardware and software components required to detect and range on specified targets and report track data to C2. The EO/IR
 sensor suite consists of five (5) gimbaled EO sensors located on the cardinal faces of the deckhouse and associated electronics in Electronic Modular Enclosures (EMEs). Also included are Detect and Tracking
 Software components that provide embedded control and generate tracks for the C2 system and Mine Like Object (MLO) detection algorithm.

