 Justification:
 The FY 2027 primary efforts are: Center Wing Box (CWB) replacement (Exhibit 8578), NP2000/8-Bladed propeller (Exhibit 3773), and Low Cost Modifications (Exhibit 99999X):

 - CWB replacements resumed in 2026 with the procurement of two kits for installation in 2028. Two additional kits will be procured in 2027 for installation in 2029.

 - NP-2000/8-Bladed Propeller completed installations on 90 C-130H aircraft in July 2025. The 2027 funding supports Interim Contractor Support.




