 Modification adds a Global Positioning System (GPS) receiver and an improved Inertial Measurement Unit (IMU) to improve the missile's capability for the Destruction of Enemy Air Defenses (DEAD) mission.

 Funding for this exhibit contained in PE 0207162F.

 Justification:
